      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "URGING (2) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won two of four starts. Was out of the placings last time (25.05) at Sale in a Grade 5, finishing fifth and beaten 4.5 lengths. Has the ability and should feature. LIVIN' LAVISH (8) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 5th (23.32) at this track. The form out of last race has been strong. Warrants plenty of respect. LET IT LINGER (3) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished second (17.14) at Healesville latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Has a good record here including four wins. Will give a great sight again. JUMBUK JOZEF (6) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
